  "text": "BBCSs have been introduced for low-cost, low-power, and large-scale wireless networks. Due to the prominent characteristics, BBCSs have been adopted in many applications such as wireless sensor networks, IoT, and smart agriculture [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] .",
